44:11.694 --> 44:13.694
But we have many Satya Narayana Pujas.

44:15.008 --> 44:18.663
For all these Satya Narayanas, Sahaja Yogis are not supposed to go.

44:19.775 --> 44:22.032
They can only go to Narayana Puja

44:22.689 --> 44:26.504
because Satya Narayana is that path which is added to it

44:27.537 --> 44:30.203
for camouflaging, is meant for these

44:30.280 --> 44:34.462
horrible Brahmins who make you pay. For what?

44:37.847 --> 44:41.970
Sahaja Yogis are not allowed to go to Satya Narayana Puja.

44:42.278 --> 44:47.350
They can have Narayana Puja. And what is Narayana ultimately becomes?

44:48.226 --> 44:56.011
In the Nabhi Chakra Narayana existed since He was created by the Devi.

44:57.926 --> 44:59.401
And It looks after

45:01.439 --> 45:04.982
the seeking, the nourishing of the seeking like a father,

45:05.961 --> 45:10.608
and then It incarnates again and then It incarnates again

45:10.680 --> 45:14.606
to help our seeking to a higher position and a higher position

45:15.377 --> 45:23.131
till it reaches a point where you start seeking God Almighty.

45:23.951 --> 45:28.911
Then you jump into the Shakti of Mahalakshmi.

45:29.349 --> 45:33.587
Then you are in the hands of Mahalakshmi Shakti.

45:34.085 --> 45:38.325
Means Lakshmi evolves into Mahalakshmi principle.

45:42.209 --> 45:49.209
Now this Mahalakshmi principle resides in the central path of Sushumna.

45:50.670 --> 45:59.975
And this central path of Sushumna is to be established fully

46:00.394 --> 46:03.035
and awakened when the Kundalini rises.

46:03.816 --> 46:05.816
When the Kundalini does not rise,

46:06.069 --> 46:09.257
this path is kept absolutely black.

46:11.631 --> 46:17.353
It is absolutely black, there is nothing in it except for the deities

46:18.286 --> 46:21.418
who are lying without any light.

46:23.277 --> 46:27.912
When the Kundalini rises, then only these deities get awakened

46:28.802 --> 46:32.171
and when they get awakened this Sushumna path,

46:32.594 --> 46:38.417
this central path of Mahalakshmi starts acting

46:40.125 --> 46:44.913
as the balancing power, to begin with at the Nabhi chakra.

46:46.180 --> 46:51.697
So Nabhi Chakra is surrounded by ten Gurus, the Prophets

46:52.154 --> 46:53.983
who give you the balance,

46:54.304 --> 46:58.154
who come on this earth again and again to give you balance in life.

46:59.027 --> 47:01.845
They tell you, “don’t do this, don’t do that.”

47:02.009 --> 47:06.295
But we don’t listen, we don’t accept it. We may say

47:06.429 --> 47:08.974
that we follow such guru, such guru. Like,

47:09.085 --> 47:12.420
you know Muslims are. They say, “We follow Mohammed Sahib.”

47:12.987 --> 47:14.720
Now if Mohammed Sahib has said

47:14.965 --> 47:18.588
