48:08.594 --> 48:15.594
No difference. Same thing it was. We can prove it in Sahaja Yoga.

48:17.342 --> 48:22.045
We can prove it, how important it is that we should know

48:22.418 --> 48:23.959
that they were all the same,

48:24.673 --> 48:26.757
and that they stood for the same thing,

48:27.121 --> 48:28.501
but at a period.

48:28.582 --> 48:31.095
Now today you have got ganja,

48:31.221 --> 48:33.799
I don’t know the names also of all these things what you

48:33.948 --> 48:34.642
drink and smoke,

48:34.691 --> 48:35.596
God knows what.

48:36.285 --> 48:37.976
Human beings are really clever

48:38.204 --> 48:40.759
to get everything that can destroy you. It's like,

