then you'll find out the third thing when I die,

49:03.559 --> 49:07.181
that “Mataji didn't say this one.” So we should do it.

49:08.296 --> 49:13.435
Very intelligent. All the time destroying your central path,

49:15.342 --> 49:17.405
and nicely managing through that.

