For example, now your left Nabhi is Gruha Lakshmi.

49:47.644 --> 49:49.909
Gruha Lakshmi is the Deity of the household.

49:51.177 --> 49:53.177
But if you have too much outward type,

49:53.583 --> 49:54.740
you're running a madness.

