50:09.690 --> 50:10.637
you'll get upset.

50:11.812 --> 50:13.523
And poor this spleen has to

50:13.550 --> 50:16.394
pour in more red blood corpuscles

50:16.638 --> 50:18.431
and it becomes mad and fails you.

